      <div class="msgContentFrame">Do some leves. Then make Bone Harpoon Butt.  Got to level 7 doing this. Buy bone chips for 54 Gil and sell the butt for 174.  Easy.  At this point you should be able to make copper earrings, rings, etc easily to level. Buy the nuggets since it costs fire crystals to make nuggets which isn't worth it IMO. My server is flooded with copper accessories so harder to make a profit, but you should be able to break even or make money.  </div>
